# BlackHole 2ch bundled installer (optional)
#
# To enable offline BlackHole installation, download the official .pkg from:
#   https://github.com/ExistentialAudio/BlackHole/releases/tag/v0.6.0
#
# Place BlackHole2ch.v0.6.0.pkg in this directory.
# electron-builder will include it as an extraResource at build time.
# At runtime, the app checks for this file first before downloading.
#
# Without the bundled pkg the app falls back to downloading from GitHub.
